		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.scottsbasslessons.com/?p=9035#comment-15700</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[I recently send out a bass-amp-questionnaire to the worldwide bass playing community. To find out exactly what players are using and why. Some interesting results there! Ampeg, Fender and Gallien Krueger are the top 3 of most used bass amps, probably with good reason, so check them out if looking for something new. Markbass, Aguilar and Eden are definitely worth some listening to as well.
You can check the full results of the questionnaire here:
http://debontamps.com/bass-amp-questionnaire/]]></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>I recently send out a bass-amp-questionnaire to the worldwide bass playing community. To find out exactly what players are using and why. Some interesting results there! Ampeg, Fender and Gallien Krueger are the top 3 of most used bass amps, probably with good reason, so check them out if looking for something new. Markbass, Aguilar and Eden are definitely worth some listening to as well.<br />
You can check the full results of the questionnaire here:<br />
<a href="http://debontamps.com/bass-amp-questionnaire/" rel="nofollow">http://debontamps.com/bass-amp-questionnaire/</a></p>
